<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-12-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-12-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="267" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d267">
                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Egan</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Blaine</persName></hi>.</head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Santiago</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-12-24"><hi rend="italic">December 24,
                            1891</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Mr. Egan acknowledges the instructions relating to publicity of dispatches
                        and says that he will strictly comply and has exercised the greatest care in
                        that respect.</p>
                </div>
